Class UserDecomposer.Decomposition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mdbook.UserDecomposer.Decomposition
  • Enclosing class:
    UserDecomposer

    public static class UserDecomposer.Decomposition
extends java.lang.Object
    Equivalent of a User object, but with its components converted to JSONObjects and grouped into HashMaps based on their types. Makes it easier to store in Elasticsearch.
    See Also:
